data.description: PRICE ALERT!!!   LOCATION & VIEWS... just 10 minutes from downtown Wenatchee.  Marvel at the mountains or relish the river views from this amazing 2400+ sq. ft. home that sits on just over an acre.  Natural sunlight enhances almost every room.  Two bedrooms on main level, primary suite on upper level. A previous Microsoft employee and owner upgraded the master bath with jacuzzi tub, shower, beautiful double sinks and mirror. Also the king size master bedroom with lots of closet space, high ceilings creating a majestic view. Must see! Hunter Douglas blinds throughout. Entertain on the deck that looks out towards the Columbia River and Wenatchee. Ideal space for a small vineyard on backside of home. Hot tub included. RV parking. NO CCR's!
